00:35:15,680 --> 00:35:18,280
 I,

677
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:20,980
 kak smo bili velika obite,

678
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:23,040
 nakon krunica smo svi dobili jabuku,

679
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:23,440
 znači,

680
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,200
 nije bilo ko danas,

681
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:25,340
 imaš svega na izobilju,

682
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:26,480
 pa jedi koliko te volja.

683
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:26,900
 Nema,

684
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:27,820
 nego kak je,

685
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:28,220
 red,

686
00:35:28,220 --> 00:35:28,820
 tak je red.

687
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:30,860
 Ja sam jedva čekala da odvrte,

688
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,080
 da dobijem svoju jabuku,

689
00:35:32,080 --> 00:35:33,180
 briga me za krunicu.

690
00:35:33,180 --> 00:35:34,740
 Uglavnom,

691
00:35:34,740 --> 00:35:36,700
 od toga da mi je bila tlaka,

692
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,880
 sad dođem u Međugorje

693
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:40,680
 i slušam gospine poruke.

694
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:41,680
 Post,

695
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:43,140
 molitva,

696
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:44,620
 ispovjed,

697
00:35:45,100 --> 00:35:45,820
 klanjanje,

698
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:49,020
 pa di sam ja do sad bila u vjeri,

699
00:35:49,020 --> 00:35:50,520
 ja sam mislila da nešto znam.

700
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:53,460
 Ajmo sad drugi vitam uvest.

701
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:55,180
 Molitva krunice,

702
00:35:55,180 --> 00:35:57,540
 ali ta krunica koja je mišna na živce,

703
00:35:57,540 --> 00:35:58,660
 molitva krunica.

704
00:35:58,660 --> 00:36:00,260
 Po tim dosadnim,

705
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,340
 vjernim činima,

706
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,600
 gledajte,

707
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,620
 dosadnim na prvu,

708
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:04,640
 vjernim činima,

709
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:07,500
 je Bog gledao stav moga srca.

710
00:36:08,620 --> 00:36:10,000
 Stav iznutra.

711
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:12,100
 Ja ću biti vjerna

712
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:14,060
 u ovome što Bog kaže,

713
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:15,420
 to tak treba biti.

714
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:17,340
 Ja ću se truditi tako.

715
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:19,160
 I onda sam išla,

716
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:20,460
 kak sam radila po 12 sati,

717
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:20,940
 svaki dan,

718
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:23,400
 onda sam išla svaka tri mjeseca negde u Međugorje.

719
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:26,600
 To mi je bilo jako, jako ljekovito za srce.

720
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:28,680
 Tada sam prvi puta u Međugorje,

721
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:29,160
 kad sam bila,

722
00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:30,360
 sam predala život Bogu.

723
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:32,260
 Nisam ni znala da je to novo rođenje,

724
00:36:32,260 --> 00:36:33,620
 pojma nisam imala,

725
00:36:33,620 --> 00:36:36,720
 ali sam prvi puta svjesno rekla Bogu da.

726
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:38,900
 I od onda,

727
00:36:38,900 --> 00:36:39,460
 znaš ono,

728
00:36:39,460 --> 00:36:40,720
 kad te gospa zakrili

729
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:43,820
 i kad te počne svojo milošću pogorivati

730
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:45,020
 u pravim smjerovima.

731
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:47,380
 Ja sam dolazila u situacije,

732
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:49,080
 dolazi otac Ralf Diorio,

733
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:50,560
 opet, prvi susred,

734
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:53,480
 ekstra karizmatsko iz Amerike,

735
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:55,100
 svećani karizmatske obnove,

736
00:36:55,100 --> 00:36:56,340
 on u Međugorju.

737
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:58,440
 Mi vozimo cijelu noš da tam dođemo,

738
00:36:58,440 --> 00:36:59,960
 tražim ga po Međugorju,

739
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,700
 a on je sa strane tamo,

740
00:37:01,700 --> 00:37:03,460
 nekad je bil neki omladinski,

741
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:04,180
 nevam nija pojma,

742
00:37:04,180 --> 00:37:04,420
