743
00:37:06,180 --> 00:37:07,060
 Čovjek krene,

744
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:08,740
 zadnje predavanje stignemo,

745
00:37:08,740 --> 00:37:09,420
 zadnje.

746
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:12,640
 On priča kako da se pripremimo za molitvu

747
00:37:12,640 --> 00:37:14,140
 i što da očekujemo,

748
00:37:14,140 --> 00:37:16,900
 što Bog želi dati djeci svojoj koju voli.

749
00:37:16,900 --> 00:37:18,520
 Meni se to,

750
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:20,840
 ako da mi neko lijepi nešto ovako za mene,

751
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:23,100
 meni se to tak lijepi unutra u srcu.

752
00:37:23,100 --> 00:37:25,740
 Na nekom velikom igralištu,

753
00:37:25,740 --> 00:37:27,260
 čovjek krene moliti,

754
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:28,840
 ljudi krenu padati ko kruške.

755
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:30,280
 Isu se, šta je sad pak ovo?

756
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:31,540
 Šta im je?

757
00:37:31,540 --> 00:37:33,560
 Je li ih nešto boli?

758
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:34,940
 Je pao nesvijest?

759
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:36,160
 Ja nemam pojma,

760
00:37:36,160 --> 00:37:37,200
 šta je ovo?

761
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:39,640
 Ali ljudi se slažu ko kruške.

762
00:37:39,640 --> 00:37:40,260
 Znači ono,

763
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:42,160
 takva sila duha svetoga,

764
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:43,520
 to je nevjerojatno.

765
00:37:43,520 --> 00:37:44,520
 Moja mama,

766
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:46,800
 moja mama se složila ko klada,

767
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:47,880
 45 minuta se mrnula,

768
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:49,460
 nije s onog poda.

769
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:51,100
 Moja kuma na drugu stranu,

770
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:52,320
 ja ono,

771
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:53,380
 ne znam di ću.

772
00:37:53,380 --> 00:37:54,700
 Dođe do mene,

773
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:56,480
 prvi puta u životu,

774
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:58,900
 kao ako možeš zamisliti,

775
00:37:58,900 --> 00:38:00,500
 znači ja imam 90 i nešto kila,

776
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:01,880
 ja kad stojim na svojim nogama,

777
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,640
 dobro osjetim svoju kilažu.

778
00:38:03,640 --> 00:38:04,920
 Znači,

779
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:07,480
 kao da nemaš grama,

780
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,960
 težine,

781
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:11,800
 neka milina kroz tijelo.

782
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,080
 Znači nema grama,

783
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:14,240
 nema težine tijela,

784
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:16,600
 nego sila od ozgo

785
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:18,360
 i milina koja prolazi,

786
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:20,020
 to polina milina koja prolazi.

787
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:21,220
 Ja stojim ovako,

788
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,260
 ne znam uopće kako stojim,

789
00:38:22,260 --> 00:38:23,460
 ne znam na čim nogama stojim,

790
00:38:23,460 --> 00:38:24,120
 samo stojim.

791
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:25,120
 Evo, nisam pala,

792
00:38:25,120 --> 00:38:26,080
 ostajem tak stajati.

793
00:38:26,080 --> 00:38:26,680
 I stojim,

794
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:27,520
 i stojim,

795
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:28,620
 i ujuškam se,

796
00:38:28,620 --> 00:38:29,620
 i tak stojim,

797
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:30,520
 i nemam pojma

798
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:32,060
 koliko vremena tak stojim.

799
00:38:32,060 --> 00:38:33,000
 Znači,

800
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:34,880
 jedno,

801
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:37,340
 opet jedna nova prekretnica

802
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,660
 nakon tog Međugorja.

803
00:38:38,660 --> 00:38:39,360
 Znači,

804
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,980
 Bog nas traži,

805
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:42,660
 kakvi god da smo,

806
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:44,780
 u kojoj god jami da smo bili,

807
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:46,800
 Bog nas traži.

808
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:47,640
 Kasnije,

809
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:48,500
 znači,

810
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:49,820
 puno tih seminara,

811
00:38:49,820 --> 00:38:51,080
 Ivančić zvijezdan,

812
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:52,140
 puno tih seminara,

813
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:54,220
 i kasnije dolazi,

814
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:56,960
 pred kraj 90-ih,

815
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:57,520
 dolazi

816
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,760
 Paterufus.

817
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,960
 Nema mjesta,

818
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:02,240
 ja čujem ja tu najavu,

819
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:03,560
 nema mjesta,

820
00:39:03,560 --> 00:39:05,480
 ja dolazim na siget,

821
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,340
 onako zadnja,

822
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:07,300
 misli si Bože,

823
00:39:07,740 --> 00:39:09,020
 ovo mi zvuči zanimljivo,

824
00:39:09,020 --> 00:39:09,820
 ja ne znam,

