00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:11,440
 ali zvuči mi zanimljivo,

826
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:13,420
 ozdravljenje i oslobađanje,

827
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:15,040
 ja nemam pojma puno o tome,

828
00:39:15,040 --> 00:39:15,920
 ali zvuči zanimljivo.

