870
00:40:30,380 --> 00:40:31,880
 onda sam krenula u kontra,

871
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:32,900
 u ljutnju,

872
00:40:32,900 --> 00:40:34,160
 u bjez,

873
00:40:34,160 --> 00:40:35,260
 u povrijeđenost,

874
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:36,740
 u osvetoljubivost,

875
00:40:36,740 --> 00:40:37,820
 u mržnju,

876
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:39,760
 znači katastrofa,

877
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,860
 to je katastrofa

878
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:41,780
 na drugi način.

879
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:44,740
 i taj semljar je odlomio,

