 ili kad napravi neku glupost,

1845
01:16:18,820 --> 01:16:20,060
 ili ga hiti kroz prozor.

1846
01:16:20,060 --> 01:16:22,880
 Pa ali tako je,

1847
01:16:22,880 --> 01:16:23,840
 drastično govorim,

1848
01:16:23,840 --> 01:16:24,720
 ali je tako.

1849
01:16:24,720 --> 01:16:26,560
 I kad pogriješi,

1850
01:16:26,560 --> 01:16:27,520
 i kad slomi nešto,

1851
01:16:27,520 --> 01:16:28,880
 i kad napravi neku glupost,

1852
01:16:28,880 --> 01:16:30,080
 i kad kaže krivu riječ,

1853
01:16:30,080 --> 01:16:31,760
 i kad se loše ponaša,

1854
01:16:31,760 --> 01:16:34,340
 pokušaš najbolje što znaš

1855
01:16:34,340 --> 01:16:35,320
 odgajat ga,

1856
01:16:35,380 --> 01:16:36,540
 privlačit ga,

1857
01:16:36,540 --> 01:16:37,100
 učit ga,

1858
01:16:37,100 --> 01:16:37,980
 ponavljat mu,

1859
01:16:37,980 --> 01:16:39,360
 stavljat mu granice.

1860
01:16:39,360 --> 01:16:40,220
 Znači,

1861
01:16:40,220 --> 01:16:41,320
 Bog nas uči,

1862
01:16:41,320 --> 01:16:43,240
 ali nas ne uništava.

1863
01:16:43,240 --> 01:16:44,320
 On je za nas.

1864
01:16:44,320 --> 01:16:46,180
 Za naše dobro.

1865
01:16:46,180 --> 01:16:48,120
 I tako,

1866
01:16:48,120 --> 01:16:48,820
 pokaj se,

1867
01:16:48,820 --> 01:16:50,820
 primi to svjetlo,

1868
01:16:50,820 --> 01:16:51,840
 primi tu milost,

1869
01:16:51,840 --> 01:16:52,960
 iznesi.

1870
01:16:52,960 --> 01:16:53,440
 Znači,

1871
01:16:53,440 --> 01:16:55,140
 prvo uvijek ga veličaj prvo.

1872
01:16:55,140 --> 01:16:57,060
 Uvijek ga prvo veličaj.

1873
01:16:57,060 --> 01:16:58,580
 I za to ga se pokaj.

1874
01:16:58,580 --> 01:17:01,020
 Moli duha svetoga ti donese svjetlo,

1875
01:17:01,020 --> 01:17:03,280
 šta trebaš istresti svoga srca.

1876
01:17:03,280 --> 01:17:05,640
 i onda izli srce pred njim.

1877
01:17:05,640 --> 01:17:06,600
 Nekad ljude,

1878
01:17:06,600 --> 01:17:08,560
 ja malo opominjem kod nas.

1879
01:17:08,560 --> 01:17:10,120
 Ljudi se sakriju,

1880
01:17:10,120 --> 01:17:10,620
 ne,

1881
01:17:10,620 --> 01:17:11,600
 ja molim krunicu,

1882
01:17:11,600 --> 01:17:12,600
 da me krivo ne razumijete,

1883
01:17:12,600 --> 01:17:13,940
 o naši u devet sati mole,

1884
01:17:13,940 --> 01:17:16,780
 cijeli ovaj mjesec krunicu za mir u svijetu

1885
01:17:16,780 --> 01:17:17,740
 i za mir,

1886
01:17:17,740 --> 01:17:19,300
 i za ono izbavljenje,

1887
01:17:19,300 --> 01:17:19,900
 isciljenje,

1888
01:17:19,900 --> 01:17:23,100
 ali prvenstveno za mir na poziv pape i gospe.

1889
01:17:23,100 --> 01:17:24,180
 Znači,

1890
01:17:24,180 --> 01:17:24,980
 molim krunicu,

1891
01:17:24,980 --> 01:17:25,400
 ali,

1892
01:17:25,400 --> 01:17:27,560
 znam nam se dogodi da se sakrijemo,

1893
01:17:27,560 --> 01:17:28,620
 pogotovo starijima,

1894
01:17:28,620 --> 01:17:30,520
 da se sakriju iza krunice,

1895
01:17:30,520 --> 01:17:32,560
 da se sakriju iza pobožnosti.

1896
01:17:32,560 --> 01:17:33,660
 Šta si radila?

1897
01:17:33,660 --> 01:17:34,260
 Molila sam.

1898
01:17:34,260 --> 01:17:34,960
 Znači,

1899
01:17:34,960 --> 01:17:36,420
 imam u susjedstvu ljude,

1900
01:17:36,420 --> 01:17:37,080
 molila sam,

1901
01:17:37,080 --> 01:17:38,760
 pa onda na svaku treću

1902
01:17:38,760 --> 01:17:39,520
 otepe

1903
01:17:39,520 --> 01:17:40,800
 onu prostu riječ.

1904
01:17:40,800 --> 01:17:41,580
 Pa čekaj,

1905
01:17:41,580 --> 01:17:42,860
 ako si molila sati,

1906
01:17:42,860 --> 01:17:43,360
 pol, dva,

1907
01:17:43,360 --> 01:17:46,000
 pa kako ti lete tolke prostote cijeli dan?

1908
01:17:46,000 --> 01:17:47,440
 Pa daj se saberi.

1909
01:17:47,440 --> 01:17:48,360
 Znači,

1910
01:17:48,360 --> 01:17:49,480
 promijeni tu molitvu,

1911
01:17:49,480 --> 01:17:50,940
 daj istresi malo sebe.

1912
01:17:50,940 --> 01:17:52,800
 Daj kaži iskreno,

1913
01:17:52,800 --> 01:17:53,240
 gospodine,

1914
01:17:53,240 --> 01:17:55,880
 pa daj mi pomozi da se otkačim ovoga.

1915
01:17:55,880 --> 01:17:57,780
 Pa svi mi smo u izazovu.

1916
01:17:57,780 --> 01:18:01,020
 Pa neprijatelj nas napada svakakim stvarima.

1917
01:18:01,020 --> 01:18:02,380
 Da se ljutimo,

1918
01:18:02,380 --> 01:18:03,060
 da sudimo,

1919
01:18:03,060 --> 01:18:03,960
 da grabimo,

1920
01:18:03,960 --> 01:18:04,940
 da smo zavidni,

1921
01:18:04,940 --> 01:18:06,200
 da ogovaramo,

1922
01:18:06,200 --> 01:18:07,580
 da zamuljavamo,

1923
01:18:07,580 --> 01:18:08,580
 da smo oholi,

1924
01:18:08,580 --> 01:18:09,460
 da smo bahati,

1925
01:18:09,520 --> 01:18:10,480
 ja vrlo često,

1926
01:18:10,480 --> 01:18:11,900
 od kako je gospodin to opomenuo,

1927
01:18:11,900 --> 01:18:14,520
 vrlo često vježbam sebe.

1928
01:18:14,520 --> 01:18:15,820
 Vježbam sebe.

1929
01:18:15,820 --> 01:18:16,080
 Znači,

1930
01:18:16,080 --> 01:18:18,040
 pronalazim se nekad u danu,

1931
01:18:18,040 --> 01:18:19,420
 20, 30 puta,

1932
01:18:19,420 --> 01:18:21,600
 kako mi misao ide ukrivo.

1933
01:18:21,600 --> 01:18:23,820
 Kako želim izgunđat na nekoga.

1934
01:18:23,820 --> 01:18:25,420
 Kako želim osudit.

1935
01:18:25,420 --> 01:18:27,720
 Kako želim promrmljati nešto što nije dobro.

1936
01:18:27,720 --> 01:18:28,240
 A kažem,

1937
01:18:28,240 --> 01:18:29,340
 e, nećeš ono.

1938
01:18:29,340 --> 01:18:30,160
 Sama je sebi,

1939
01:18:30,160 --> 01:18:31,380
 doslovce ko u autu,

1940
01:18:31,380 --> 01:18:32,900
 kad vidiš da ideš u krivom smjeru,

1941
01:18:32,900 --> 01:18:34,320
 me je to gospodin pokazao.

1942
01:18:34,320 --> 01:18:35,380
 Navigacija,

1943
01:18:35,380 --> 01:18:36,680
 kad kreneš ukrivo,

1944
01:18:36,980 --> 01:18:39,300
 preusmjerava se i oće te vratiti nazad.

1945
01:18:39,300 --> 01:18:39,860
 Je li tako?

1946
01:18:39,860 --> 01:18:42,220
 Kad nešto napraviš u prometu što nije dobro,

1947
01:18:42,220 --> 01:18:43,400
 što prirodno radiš?

1948
01:18:43,400 --> 01:18:45,160
 Što radiš prirodno?

1949
01:18:45,160 --> 01:18:46,960
 Je li tako?

1950
01:18:46,960 --> 01:18:47,780
 Je li to prirodno?

1951
01:18:47,780 --> 01:18:48,840
 Ne razmišljaš,

1952
01:18:48,840 --> 01:18:50,720
 e, sam mi je izašao auto,

1953
01:18:50,720 --> 01:18:52,840
 možda bi bilo dobro da zakočim.

1954
01:18:52,840 --> 01:18:53,700
 He he,

1955
01:18:53,700 --> 01:18:55,260
 vidimo se na nebu.

1956
01:18:55,260 --> 01:18:56,060
 Znači,

1957
01:18:56,060 --> 01:19:01,040
 automatska radnja ti je kočnica,

1958
01:19:01,040 --> 01:19:01,620
 je li tako?

1959
01:19:01,620 --> 01:19:02,520
 Kočnica.

1960
01:19:02,520 --> 01:19:06,460
 E pa isto to će te vježbat svoju nutrinu,

1961
01:19:06,460 --> 01:19:08,160
 vježbat će te svoj um,

1962
01:19:08,160 --> 01:19:09,920
 vježbat će te svoj duh,

1963
01:19:09,920 --> 01:19:13,000
 da isto to radiš i kad vidiš da počinješ gunđat,

1964
01:19:13,000 --> 01:19:14,260
 da počinješ sudit,

1965
01:19:14,260 --> 01:19:15,680
 da počinješ prigovarat,

1966
01:19:15,680 --> 01:19:16,920
 da si ljubomorna,

1967
01:19:16,920 --> 01:19:18,240
 da te hvata zavist,

1968
01:19:18,240 --> 01:19:20,220
 da ti bludne misli prolaze.

1969
01:19:20,220 --> 01:19:22,280
 Znači, isto to ćeš radit.

1970
01:19:22,280 --> 01:19:23,280
 Potegni ručnu,

1971
01:19:23,280 --> 01:19:24,500
 stisni nožnu kočnicu,

1972
01:19:24,500 --> 01:19:25,160
 zaustavi se,

1973
01:19:25,160 --> 01:19:26,060
 reci samo sebi,

1974
01:19:26,060 --> 01:19:26,740
 ne može,

1975
01:19:26,740 --> 01:19:29,220
 slava Otcu i Sinu i Duhu Svetomu.

1976
01:19:29,220 --> 01:19:30,000
 Opet nislao,

1977
01:19:30,000 --> 01:19:32,080
 slava Otcu i Sinu i Duhu Svetomu.

1978
01:19:32,080 --> 01:19:33,460
 Tristo puta ako treba.

1979
01:19:33,460 --> 01:19:35,000
 Džavo će sigurno odstupiti,

1980
01:19:35,000 --> 01:19:36,280
 da će ova budala nestaje.

1981
01:19:36,280 --> 01:19:37,760
 Moli, tristo puta,

1982
01:19:37,760 --> 01:19:38,500
 slava Otcu,

1983
01:19:38,500 --> 01:19:39,880
 daj Bože da je pustim na miru.

1984
01:19:39,880 --> 01:19:41,500
 Razumijete?

1985
01:19:41,500 --> 01:19:43,000
 Vježba,

1986
01:19:43,000 --> 01:19:44,440
 to je ta disciplina.

1987
01:19:44,440 --> 01:19:46,420
 Krenite sa malim stvarima.

1988
01:19:46,420 --> 01:19:49,160
 Uzmi ono što ti je najmanjkavije,

1989
01:19:49,160 --> 01:19:51,020
 ono gdje si najslabija.

1990
01:19:51,020 --> 01:19:52,520
 Ono, otkopaj.

1991
01:19:52,520 --> 01:19:53,820
 Otkopaj.

1992
01:19:53,820 --> 01:19:55,620
 Jer mi imamo grijehe koje možda

1993
01:19:55,620 --> 01:19:57,240
 deset godina ispovjedamo.

1994
01:19:57,240 --> 01:19:58,240
 Iste grijehe.

1995
01:19:58,680 --> 01:19:59,800
 Ajde, otkopaj to.

1996
01:19:59,800 --> 01:20:02,480
 Ajde, vidi što zapravo tradiš.

1997
01:20:02,480 --> 01:20:04,360
 Ja sam sad u Duhovnim vježbama,

1998
01:20:04,360 --> 01:20:05,840
 mi idemo svake godine sa vodstvom,

1999
01:20:05,840 --> 01:20:07,960
 sad u Duhovnim vježbama sam vidjela neke stvari,

2000
01:20:07,960 --> 01:20:10,740
 iako sam puno puta prošla,

2001
01:20:10,740 --> 01:20:12,080
 sad sam vidjela neke stvari

2002
01:20:12,080 --> 01:20:13,140
 koje nikad prije nisam.

2003
01:20:13,140 --> 01:20:14,760
 Otkopaj.

2004
01:20:14,760 --> 01:20:17,940
 Ajde, šta to ja još skrivam u dubinama?

2005
01:20:17,940 --> 01:20:19,100
 Ajmo vi to vidjeti.

2006
01:20:19,100 --> 01:20:20,440
 Ajmo to proraditi.

2007
01:20:20,440 --> 01:20:22,640
 Ajmo nazvat stvari kako se stvarno zovu.

2008
01:20:22,640 --> 01:20:24,440
 I znate što najčešće bude?

2009
01:20:24,440 --> 01:20:26,440
 Ispod svih ovih stvari,

2010
01:20:26,440 --> 01:20:30,460
 bahato, samovolja, dokazivanje, uljepšavanje,

2011
01:20:30,460 --> 01:20:32,000
 lovna lajkove,

2012
01:20:32,000 --> 01:20:35,120
 šta god, nazovite kako god u današnjem riječniku,

2013
01:20:35,860 --> 01:20:37,840
 ispod toga ćete vidjeti nekoliko stvari

2014
01:20:37,840 --> 01:20:38,720
 koje su jako bitne.

2015
01:20:38,720 --> 01:20:41,760
 Čežnja za prihvaćenošću.

2016
01:20:41,760 --> 01:20:44,200
 Čežnja za ljubavju.

2017
01:20:44,200 --> 01:20:49,180
 Čežnja da se potvrdi naša vrijednost.

2018
01:20:49,180 --> 01:20:53,240
 I onda, umjesto da bauljamo sve ovo,

2019
01:20:53,240 --> 01:20:56,040
 počni od Boga tražiti ovo.

2020
01:20:56,040 --> 01:20:59,360
 Ja kad sam shvatila da je krater

2021
01:20:59,360 --> 01:21:01,240
 s onim što sam vam rekla,

2022
01:21:01,240 --> 01:21:02,640
 sam počela mojeg gospodine,

2023
01:21:02,640 --> 01:21:04,120
 samo ti to možeš nadoknaditi.

2024
01:21:04,700 --> 01:21:05,740
 Samo ti to možeš nadoknaditi.

2025
01:21:05,740 --> 01:21:06,980
 Ja trebam tvoju ljubav.

2026
01:21:06,980 --> 01:21:08,020
 Ti si ljubav.

2027
01:21:08,020 --> 01:21:08,700
 Bog je ljubav.

2028
01:21:08,700 --> 01:21:10,020
 Riječ kaže Bog je ljubav.

2029
01:21:10,020 --> 01:21:11,180
 Riječ kaže Bog je ljubav.

2030
01:21:11,180 --> 01:21:13,140
 Sad kao ljubav, izlitu ljubav,

2031
01:21:13,140 --> 01:21:13,960
 jer ja trebam.

2032
01:21:13,960 --> 01:21:15,160
 Ja to trebam.

2033
01:21:15,160 --> 01:21:16,320
 Ti si me tako ustvorio.

2034
01:21:16,320 --> 01:21:17,580
 Ja to trebam.

2035
01:21:17,580 --> 01:21:18,960
 Trebam.

2036
01:21:18,960 --> 01:21:20,220
 Dijete dođe, tati kaže,

2037
01:21:20,220 --> 01:21:21,580
 žedan sam, gladan sam.

2038
01:21:21,580 --> 01:21:22,980
 Tata, daj mi vode.

2039
01:21:22,980 --> 01:21:24,100
 Tata, žedan sam.

2040
01:21:24,100 --> 01:21:25,740
 Tata, žedan sam.

2041
01:21:25,740 --> 01:21:28,340
 Zašto ne bi ja isto?

2042
01:21:28,340 --> 01:21:31,200
 Razumijete?

2043
01:21:31,200 --> 01:21:32,580
 To vam je to.

2044
01:21:33,540 --> 01:21:34,980
 Amen.

